What is the one message that has never made it out of your draft? 📫

From a spontaneous tattoo appointment, to full-on existential reflection (literally), our London Notion community really showed up and had a lot to share (PSA: some convos may have been too deep for a weekday evening).

Huge shoutout to our lovely London Notion team & ambassadors, alongside with @workdotlife - for bringing the @notionhq Mail Launch event from draft to delivered! 📮

Introducing Enterprise Search 🔎 One search for everything.

Now you can find answers across 3x more apps (MS Teams, SharePoint, OneDrive, Gmail, Box, Salesforce, Zendesk, Slack, Google Drive, GitHub, Jira, Linear) and also uncover things hidden in PDFs and databases.
